data.description:
www.6116Southwell.com - Stately Newmark Home showcases 20' ceilings in Foyer w/wood flooring extending into Formal Dining & Study. Den boasts cast-stone, gas-log fireplace & ceramic tile that flows into the Gourmet Kitchen, which features an abundance of cabinetry & counter space, butlers pantry, island, & breakfast bar. Spacious Master Suite with bay window. Luxurious Master Bath boasts oversized shower, jetted tub, dual raised vanities & dual closets. Media Room! Backyard paradise with pool & plenty of green space!

Please visit my MLS Site http://Search.RealtyByMonica.com for more current listings or my buyer's website http://BuyRealEstateWithMonica.com for Buyer info and testimonials. Check out my fan page http://RealtyByMonicaFanPage.com for the latest news.
